# Project Name: TAPA - Technologically Augmented Personal Assistant

## Primary Goals
- Simplify the understanding and usage of LLMs for non-technical users.
- Provide a centralized platform for interacting with multiple AI models.
- Offer an engaging and educational experience through a friendly mascot.

## Tech Stack & Environment

**Frontend:** Vite + React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
**Backend:** Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth)

## UI/UX Design

### Look & Feel
- Friendly and approachable design with a focus on simplicity and clarity. Make all the designs beautiful and not cookie cutter.

Use @phosphor-icons/react for icons. Do not install other packages for icons, themes,  etc. Unless is necessary or I request them.